`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"Located in Chennais Taramani ecosystem, IIT Madras routinely tops national rankings and operates Indias first university-based research park. Labs like Robert Bosch Centre for Data Science and AI (RBCDSAI), Centre for Innovation (CFI), and advanced manufacturing facilities make IITM attractive to both theory-heavy and build-heavy profiles. Compare the rest of the IIT network at the IIT internships hub to see how Madras differs on depth and industry proximity."}),`
